<activity xml:id="act-componerNuevasUnidades" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ol>
      <li>In Han’s algorithm, the 14 tens were recorded as 140. In Elena’s algorithm, we record 4 in the tens place that represents 40 and 100 is placed at the top of the problem to show the new hundred.</li>
      <li><p>
</p><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Addition." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148951.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Addition." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-148951.svg" width="80%"/>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


